{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.240", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.000", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gesch\u00e4tzte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.560", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.840", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allzu oft bem\u00fcht die Politik den Satz: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.880", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Handwerk hat goldenen Boden.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.240", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bringe den Satz heute deshalb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.200", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.200", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Satz durchaus Verpflichtung f\u00fcr die Politik ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.240", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir hier sitzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.680", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben die Aufgabe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.160", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rahmenbedingungen daf\u00fcr zu schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.880", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Unternehmer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.640", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Handwerker in unserem Land gut existieren und arbeiten k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.480", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben die Aufgabe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.320", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rahmenbedingungen zu schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Handwerker rechtssicher agieren k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.520", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben selbstverst\u00e4ndlich auch die Verpflichtung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.120", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sorge daf\u00fcr zu tragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.000", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir vor allem die Handwerksbetriebe nicht mit \u00fcberbordender B\u00fcrokratie erdr\u00fccken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.560", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir sind uns alle einig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.360", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir das als Daueraufgabe begreifen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.880", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist es zun\u00e4chst einmal gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.480", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir heute im Rahmen dieses Antrags dar\u00fcber reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.520", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "R\u00fcckschau halten und bewerten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.040", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir vielleicht an der einen oder anderen Stelle \u00fcber das Ziel hinausgeschossen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.960", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was die B\u00fcrokratie angeht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.160", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei Ihrem Antrag haben Sie den Bereich des Widerrufsrechts, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.840", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Widerrufsbelehrung im Blick. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.080", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beim Lesen des Antrags war ich positiv gestimmt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.840", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil ich dachte: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.360", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Na ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.040", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Antrag bekennt man sich zun\u00e4chst einmal ganz klar zur Erforderlichkeit des Widerrufsrechts auch im Handwerkerbereich.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.120", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach der Kurzintervention des Kollegen war ich dann nicht mehr ganz so sicher; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.960", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn da hat das ganz anders geklungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.520", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube schon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.560", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir uns einig sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.200", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir das Widerrufsrecht auch in diesem Bereich brauchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.920", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie so oft hat dies die Politik auch auf europ\u00e4ischer Ebene nicht ohne Not geregelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.480", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es waren schwarze Schafe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.360", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die dazu gef\u00fchrt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.240", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir handeln mussten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.040", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Sorge daf\u00fcr zu tragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.960", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass nicht der Verbraucher der Leidtragende ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.920", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beispiele gibt es auch heute noch\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.120", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich habe ein paar dabei\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.880", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eWenn der Dachhai zweimal klingelt\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.400", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201e16\u00a0500\u00a0Euro f\u00fcr falsche Handwerker\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.440", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eDie Teer-Betr\u00fcger finden immer mehr Opfer\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.440", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber zun\u00e4chst einmal ist es wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.400", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir differenzieren und nicht alle Handwerker \u00fcber einen Kamm scheren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.880", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.920", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es auch im allgemeinen Verbraucherschutz wichtig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.800", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.440", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen die Verbraucher vor \u00dcberrumpelung sch\u00fctzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir dann in die unterschiedlichen Bereiche gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.640", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir eben feststellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.960", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass gerade im Baubereich oder auch im Bereich der Finanzberatungen oftmals weitreichende Entscheidungen getroffen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.120", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist es gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.720", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn die Menschen 14\u00a0Tage Zeit haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.480", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich zu \u00fcberlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.400", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob sie diesen Vertrag wirklich aufrechterhalten wollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.720", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dennoch muss das oberste Gebot die Ausgewogenheit sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.880", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen zwischen dem Verbraucherschutz auf einen Seite und der Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.960", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie hoch die b\u00fcrokratischen Anforderungen an Handwerker, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.080", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an Unternehmer maximal sein d\u00fcrfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.640", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf der anderen Seite abw\u00e4gen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.760", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie schreiben in Ihrem Antrag von \u201euferlosen Informationspflichten\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.560", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Kollege Hoppenstedt hat es schon dargestellt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.480", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist mit Sicherheit komplex; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.440", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich will das gar nicht kleinreden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.880", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber von \u201euferlos\u201c kann man nicht reden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.480", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie im Internet nachsehen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.720", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das waren nur ein paar Klicks\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.280", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann finden Sie schnell verschiedene Musterbeispiele f\u00fcr Widerrufsbelehrungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.560", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe hier ein ganz tolles Beispiel von der Handwerkskammer Frankfurt-Rhein-Main. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.640", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da ist die Widerrufsbelehrung auf einer Seite zu finden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.760", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eUferlos\u201c ist das mit Sicherheit nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.240", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern durchaus in fassbarem Umfang."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.120", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich ist die Missbrauchsgefahr da. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.400", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie einen Kunden haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.560", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der nicht zahlungswillig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.240", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann f\u00e4ngt er unter Umst\u00e4nden an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.320", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit fadenscheinigen Argumenten Gr\u00fcnde daf\u00fcr zu suchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.200", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht zu zahlen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.480", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur Ehrlichkeit geh\u00f6rt zun\u00e4chst einmal aber auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.400", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.960", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Kunde daf\u00fcr auch andere Gr\u00fcnde heranziehen kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.160", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich ist das Widerrufsrecht durchaus fehler\u00adanf\u00e4llig. "
   ]
